name: MovieMaster
0:
”Alexa, ask Movie Master to give me the upcoming movies.”
”Alexa, ask Movie Master for now playing movies.”
”Alexa, ask Movie Master for help.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie master
des: Movie Master is powered by The Movie Database API, so it is always updated. Just ask one option at a time. For example "Alexa, ask movie master for the upcoming movies." or, "Alexa, ask movie master for the now playing movies."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
